text: There is a boy on the stool. The stool is tipping over. The boy is taking cookies out of the jar. The cupboard is open. The girl is saying, putting her finger to her mouth and also putting her hand out for a cookie. The mother is washing dishes. Water is spilling over from the sink onto the floor.
